                                "jurisdiction":  "US",
                                "effectiveFrom":  "2026-01-01T00:00:00Z",
                                "summary":  "The deterministic controls for this package. Enforced as executable rules: CY-023 (the universal AI-execution-boundary / cross-tenant controls). The remaining controls are carried here for traceability; detailed field-vs-literal rule tuning is a follow-up (see the hand-authored T9-001..010 packages for the target).",
                                "contentText":  "CY-001 Approved cyber policy | Governance | Reject unapproved policy activation | Critical | CISO. CY-002 Asset inventory | Preventive | Flag unregistered asset | Critical | CISO. CY-003 Security logging | Preventive | Require logging on critical systems | Critical | CISO. CY-004 SIEM coverage | Detective | Flag coverage gap | Critical | CISO. CY-005 Alert severity mapping | Preventive | Reject unmapped severity | High | SOC. CY-006 SOC case owner | Preventive | Reject case without owner | High | SOC. CY-007 Threat intelligence source approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved source | High | CISO. CY-008 Vulnerability scanning | Detective | Require scheduled scan coverage | Critical | CISO. CY-009 Critical vulnerability SLA | Corrective | Escalate overdue remediation | Critical | CISO. CY-010 Patch exception approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved exception | Critical | CISO. CY-011 Endpoint coverage | Detective | Flag unmonitored endpoint | Critical | CISO. CY-012 Cloud configuration monitoring | Detective | Flag misconfiguration | Critical | CISO. CY-013 Network monitoring | Detective | Flag monitoring gap | Critical | CISO. CY-014 Identity-event integration | Preventive | Require identity-event correlation | Critical | CISO/Security. CY-015 Privileged activity monitoring | Detective | Flag anomalous privileged activity | Critical | Security. CY-016 Incident response plan | Governance | Require approved plan for critical systems | Critical | CISO. CY-017 Evidence preservation | Evidence | Block deletion of incident evidence | Critical | Legal. CY-018 Containment authority | Preventive | Reject unauthorized containment action | Critical | CISO. CY-019 External communication approval | Preventive | Reject unapproved external disclosure | High | CEO/CCO. CY-020 Regulatory referral through T9-006 | Preventive | Deny direct filing outside T9-006 | Critical | CCO. CY-021 No AI destructive response | Preventive | Deny AI destructive-action permission | Critical | AI Governance. CY-022 No AI privilege expansion | Preventive | Deny AI self-privilege-expansion | Critical | AI Governance. CY-023 Cross-tenant denial | Preventive | Deny | Critical | Security. CY-024 Recovery validation | Detective | Require validation before declaring restored | Critical | CISO. CY-025 Board escalation | Corrective | Escalate material incident to Board | Critical | CISO."
                            }
